description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Cooter purrs with a rating of 60, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 180, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, 2 for East, 3 for South, and Nine Lives for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/90603-42392-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [180 Votes, Top 5% Score]
